Native DIMG Loaders status
--------------------------

Format  Read  Write  ICC   MetaData  Thumb   8bits    16bits  dependency

JPG     Done  Done   Done  Done      Done    yes      N.A     libjpeg
PNG     Done  Done   Done  Done      N.A     yes      yes     libpng
TIF/EP  Done  Done   Done  Done      Done    yes      yes     libtiff
RAW     Done  N.A    N.A   Done      Done    yes      yes     libraw
PPM     Done  TODO   N.A   N.A       N.A     yes      yes     none
PGF     Done  DONE   TODO  DONE      N.A     yes      yes     libpgf
JPEG2K  Done  Done   Done  Done      N.A     yes      yes     libjasper

Others file formats are supported only in 8 bits/color/pixel using QImageFormats plugins,
or with fail-back to ImageMagick codecs (optional).
Supported formats are listed below :

Format   Read       Write      Description                          Codec

KRA      yes        no         Krita image                              kimageformat
ORA      yes        no         Krita image                              kimageformat
PSD      yes        yes        Photoshop image                          ImageMagick
XCF      yes        no         Gimp file format                         ImageMagick
EXR      yes        yes        ILM High dynamic range image             ImageMagick
PBM      yes        yes        Portable bitmap format                   ImageMagick
PGM      yes        yes        Portable graymap format                  ImageMagick
PNM      yes        yes        Portable anymap                          ImageMagick
PPM      yes        yes        Portable pixmap format                   ImageMagick
TGA      yes        yes        Truevision Targa image                   ImageMagick
PCX      yes        yes        ZSoft IBM PC Paintbrush                  ImageMagick
PCD      yes        yes        PhotoCD                                  ImageMagick
BMP      yes        yes        Windows bitmap format                    ImageMagick
RGB      yes        yes        Raw Red Green Blue                       ImageMagick
XBM      yes        yes        X Windows system bitmap                  ImageMagick
XPM      yes        yes        X Windows system pixmap                  ImageMagick
EPS      yes        yes        Adobe Encapsulated PostScript            ImageMagick
DDS      yes        yes        Microsoft Direct Draw Surface            ImageMagick
SGI      yes        yes        Irix RGB image                           ImageMagick
ICO      yes        no         Windows icon format                      ImageMagick
MNG      yes        yes        Multiple-image Network Graphics          ImageMagick
GIF      yes        yes        CompuServe Graphics Interchange Format   ImageMagick
HDR      yes        yes        Radiance RGBE image format               ImageMagick
SVG      yes        yes        Scalable Vector Graphics                 ImageMagick
WEBP     yes        yes        Weppy image format                       ImageMagick
HEIF     yes        yes        Apple High efficiency Image Format       ImageMagick
FITS     yes        yes        Flexible Image Transport System          ImageMagick

